<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text">Geomorphic and fluvial processes rather than fire primarily disturb the alliance. Response to fire depends on the presence of on- and off-site seed sources and rainfall patterns.</div>
	<table class="zebraStripe">
		
		<tr>
			<td class="key">Fire return interval</td>
			<td>Long (25-150 years)
				
			</td>
